 people processes enabling all to “make their own McKinsey” and pursue personal and professional passions inspiring teams to confidently and continuously improve their project experiences and client impact You should be able to have a fantastic career and a full life and do it in a way that works for you. Explore what work-life flexibility can be at McKinsey. More in this section Work-life flexibility You should be able to have a fantastic career and a full life and do it in a way that works for you.more Careers at McKinsey Search and apply Retrieve my draft application Contact us FAQ Privacy policy Terms of use Local language information © 1996-2016 McKinsey & Company McKinsey Insights App Our latest thinking at your fingertips. Anytime. Anywhere. Download the app or Continue to site
